ent-Cartridge48Rifle = cartridge (.48 rifle)
    .desc = A heavy intermediate cartridge of uncertain origin. Sits somewhere between a magnum round and an anti-materiel shell. Proprietary — don't expect to find it on any shelf.
ent-SpeedLoader48Rifle = speed loader (.48 rifle)
    .desc = A stripper clip pre-loaded with .48 rifle rounds. Feeds directly into the Lionhunter's internal magazine. Proprietary and hard to come by.
